---

## SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH (FLUTTER)

- Purchase draft: `purchaseDraftProvider` in `lib/features/purchase/state/purchase_draft_provider.dart`
- No `setState` for core purchase totals (UI-only state is OK)

## PROTECTED (DO NOT BREAK UNINTENTIONALLY)

- `purchaseDraftProvider`, `purchaseTotalsProvider`, `purchaseStrictBreakdownProvider`
- `tradePurchasesListProvider`, `tradePurchasesParsedProvider`, `suppliersListProvider`, `brokersListProvider`
- Client `_filterPurchasesBySearch` / supplier selection helpers used by purchase history
- Backend path prefix: `/v1/businesses/{business_id}/...` — **add** routes; do not rename without migration

## ALWAYS

- HapticFeedback: selection on main nav; medium on save where appropriate
- `ref.invalidate(...)` after mutations that affect lists, KPIs, or reports
- Loading: **skeletons / `LinearProgressIndicator` in sections**, not blocking full-screen spinners on shell tabs
- Confirm before delete or discard with unsaved changes
- Search: **≥1 character** to search; debounce ~300ms on heavy queries
- Money in UI: `NumberFormat.currency(locale: 'en_IN', symbol: '₹', ...)` or agreed `#,##,###` pattern consistently

## NEVER

- HSN mandatory on catalog create (optional for traders)
- Snackbars for field validation (use inline `errorText`)
- Emoji in PDF body
- Duplicate purchase / item entry flows — extend the canonical wizard only
- **Entry-only** queries for **trade** spend reports (KPI + report tables)
- Auto-save purchases — always preview → confirm save

